      Well by now your probably wondering  what CircusNet is all about!
      Let us be your Gateway to Cyberspace and behond. We provide USENET
      Newsgroups and PRIVATE Internet E-Mail. We provide these services
      just as if you were transmitting or receiving your favorite echomail
      conference.

      Why should you join the team at CircusNet? Presently are carrying 2200
      Newsgroups, that number grows daily! We provide gated Newsgroups and
      Internet E-Mail Services... Our areas have been groomed for your
      enjoyment and hassle free pickup and delivery. We are located just
      outside Los Angeles, CA.

      Now the BIG PLUS! You don't even need to run a BBS to Subscribe.

        QWK Packaging is also available for you non-board operators.

